data.text:
Used - Book is in Good condition with noticeable wear on the covers. Book is in a very readable condition.

Description

This Book is the One Volume Edition of the works of Gautier and includes Volume I through Volume VII. Volumes include the following:VOLUME I - One of Cleopatra's Nights;VOLUME II - The Evil Eye;VOLUME III - Avatar;VOLUME IV - Spirit Love;VOLUME V - Fortunio;VOLUME VI - Mille. De Maupin, andVOLUME VII - Four Fates.This Edition was published in 1928 by Walter J. Black, Inc. This Edition comprises only a portion of the writings of Gautier and was published to give the reader a variety of Gautier's literary thought and accomplishments. This Book has a brown leather covering with gold lettering and gold design on the front cover and spine.
